<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <!-- Swap out "Roboto" for the font(s) you want to use -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.12.0/css/all.css" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
    
    <!-- Your own CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>

<body>

<h1>
    <p class="mt-5">
        Spring Quarter Events (R.I.P)
    </p>
</h1>

<div class= "row">
    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p class="mt-5">
            This website was originally desiged to outline some of the social events we planned to host in the Spring quarter.
            <br>
            <br> 
            With coronavirus ravaging our shores and social plans, it has instead it has become a resource to look back on what could have been...
            <br>
            <br>
            It also hosts a selection of pictures from the previous quarter
            <br>
            <br>
            <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="1.jpg" alt="First Slide">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="2.jpg" alt="First Slide">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img class="d-block w-100" src="3.jpg" alt="First Slide">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </p>
    </div>

      <div class="col-sm-6">
        <p class="mt-5">
            <% for event in @events %>
                <p3><a href="/events/<%= event[:id] %>"><%= event[:title] %></a></p>
                <p4>
                    <a "/events/<%= event[:id] %>"><%= event[:date]%></a>
                     | 
                    <a "/events/<%= event[:id] %>"><%= event[:time] %></a>
                </p>
            <% end %>
        <p>
     </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>